OL,5,EAT THE BACK OF MY MINDGby Munira, 14,  
OL,6,GMadni Muslim Girls High Sch. Dewsbury  
OL,7,BI can't write, my mind's blank. I hear 
OL,8,Bideas being yelled out of my wardrobe. 
OL,9,BI open it. A hideous and overweight    
OL,10,Bmonster stands before me.              
OL,12,BSoon my mind is overflowing with ideas.
OL,13,BMore ideas than I had in mind. It is   
OL,14,Btime for it to go back in the wardrobe.
OL,16,BI go upstairs. My dad is writing his   
OL,17,Bstory and...I see a hideous and        
OL,18,Boverweight monster near his desk.      
